claim: Brigitte Macron is a high-school teacher.
premise_source_doc_sentence: Brigitte Marie-Claude Macron  (  -LSB- bri.ʒit ma.ʁi klodə ma.kʁɔ -RSB- ; née Trogneux , -LSB- tʁɔ.ɲø -RSB- , previously Auzière , -LSB- o.zjɛːʁ -RSB- ; born 13 April 1953  )  is a high-school teacher and the wife of Emmanuel Macron , the President of the French Republic .
